Red musk creepers and their zombies were first seen after the maddened [[druid]] [[Halsaime]] deployed them as weapons against the inhabitants of Eveningstar during the [[Sschindylryn invasion of Eveningstar|drow invasion]] of the mid-1480s [[DR]].{{DDO-time}} The innocent [[ranger]] [[Peron Uthe]] carried the infection from [[Thorngap]] and quickly succumbed at the [[Eveningstar War Hospital]], transforming into a zombie and infecting other patients. Only the timely intervention of [[adventurer]]s was able to save the day, along with the head priest [[Hurim Jaskyr]] developing an inoculation against the disease that allowed Peron Uthe to be safely destroyed. More zombies were found in his home of [[Uthe Lodge]] accompanying the [[dryad]] [[Sylvie]], and deep in the Thorngap at [[Thorn Hollow]] and [[Druid's Deep]] protecting Halsaime.

